dc_title_s: West Indies, Admiralty Bay, Kingston Harbour and approaches (Raster Image)
dc_description_s: Prepared and published by the National Imagery and Mapping Agency. Depths shown by isolines and soundings. Relief shown by contours, hachures, and spot heights. "Topography is from aerial photography to 1981 and survey maps to 1988." "Copyright 1997 by the United States Government. No copyright claimed under Title 17 U.S.C." "Soundings in meters." Components: A. Bequia, Admiralty Bay. Scale 1:12,487 -- B. Saint Vincent, Kingstown Harbour and approaches. Scale 1:15,003. Includes tidal information. Map No. 25483. This map is part of a collection of scanned and georeferenced nautical charts produced by the National Geospatial-Intelligence Agency (NGA).
dc_creator_sm: United States. National Imagery and Mapping Agency
dct_spatial_sm: Admiralty Bay (Saint Vincent and the Grenadines)
